ttp://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}, {\"begin\": 298, \"end\": 304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999584723746958, \"rank\": 2.3319820729050305e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An intimacy ban was in place at the Tokyo Games amid the COVID pandemic.\", \"from\": 452, \"to\": 524, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 509, \"end\": 523, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\", \"score\": 0.9998585825331231, \"rank\": 0.00012970060051582005, \"text\": \"COVID pandemic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We know the media has had a lot of fun with this story since Tokyo 2020,\\\" the body charged with organizing the sports extravaganza in the \\\"City of Love\\\" said in a statement to Reuters.\", \"from\": 526, \"to\": 711, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 703, \"end\": 710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 0.9999999626411415, \"rank\": 3.732879669708138e-08, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But for Paris 2024 the choice of these beds for the Olympic and Paralympic Village is primarily linked to a wider ambition to ensure minimal environmental impact and a second life for all equipment used during the short period of the Games.\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 954, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 722, \"end\": 732, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9976123272564121, \"rank\": 0.0023933873694262273, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpe